content: अविभाज्य {%<ab>a.</ab>%} Indivisible. --ज्यं {@--1@} Indivisibility. {@--2@} Not being liable to be partitioned; (said of certain articles which are not to be divided at the time of partition); {%<ab>e. g.</ab>%} वस्त्रं पात्रमलंकारं कृतान्नमुदकं स्त्रियः . योगक्षेमं प्रचारं च न विभाज्यं प्रचक्षते <ls>Ms. 9. 219.</ls> °ता indivisibility, unfitness for partition.
